msgstr "Schlechte Anfragen filtern"

#: src/Lib/Admin.php:419
msgid "Helps secure your site against attacks like XSS, CSRF, and Code Injections."
msgstr "Schützt Ihre Website vor Angriffen wie XSS, CSRF und Code Injections."

#: src/Lib/Admin.php:422
msgid "Disable Rest API"
msgstr "Rest API deaktivieren"

#: src/Lib/Admin.php:424
msgid "Conceals sensitive information from attackers, such as Admin user IDs, user lists, and their IDs."
msgstr ""
"Verbirgt sensible Informationen vor Angreifern, wie Admin-Benutzer-IDs, "
"Benutzerlisten und deren IDs."

